      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:4:170:6",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/170/5721",
      "text": [
        " اَلنَّصْرَانِيِّ يَمُوتُ وَ لَهُ اِبْنٌ مُسْلِمٌ قَالَ \"إِنَّ اَللَّهَ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ لَمْ يَزِدْنَا بِالْإِسْلاَمِ إِلاَّ عِزّاً فَنَحْنُ نَرِثُهُمْ وَ لاَ يَرِثُونَّا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5721 - Muhammad ibn Sinan narrated from Abdur Rahman ibn Aʿyan from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) regarding a Christian man who dies leaving behind a Muslim son.\nImam (as) said: \"Indeed, Allah (swt), the Mighty and Majestic, has only increased us in honor through Islam. Therefore, we inherit from them, but they do not inherit from us.\""
        ]
      }
    },
